                     CONTENTS OF THE EMC PHASE 1 CD



FONTS       ALL the fonts on this CD have IFF preview screens, so you simply
            have to double click on the preview screen (or access it from a
            directory utility like Directory Opus) to "see" the font!
            This basically means that you DO NOT have to install a particular
            font into an application just to see what it looks like.


The Phase 1 CD contains the following fonts...

Type1       Adobe Type 1 fonts from EMC volumes 4, 5, 6, 7 & 16.

CG          Compugraphic Scalable fonts from EMC volumes 8, 9, 10, 23 & 24.

PDraw       Professional Draw fonts from EMC volumes 18, 19 & 20.

Clipfonts   52 Full colour High resolution Clipfonts.


------------------------------------------------------------------------------


CLIPART     ALL clipart on this CD is FULLY sorted. This means that for
            example all the pieces of different "Animals" clipart are not
            simply thrown into a directory called "Animals". In the clipart
            contents listing you will notice that there is a number (enclosed
            in brackets), this tells you the number of sub directories inside
            the main directory.

            Furthermore, EVERY sub directory also contains an IFF thumbnail
            index screen. So if for example you wanted some "Frog" clipart,
            you would go into the "Animals" directory, then into the
            "Reptiles" directory, where you would be presented with
            directories for Toads, Snakes, Crocodiles etc, and obviously
            Frogs. Inside the "Frogs" directory you would find all the "Frog"
            clipart and an Thumbnail Index screen that shows you all the
            "Frog" clipart in that directory!


The Phase 1 CD contains clipart on the following subjects...

IFF         Animals(114), Fantasy(27), Music(12), People(73), Religion(12)

IFF COL     Birds, Cars, Cats, Dinosaurs, Dogs, Fish, Horses, LionKing,
            Music, Planes & Reptiles.

EPS         Animals, Buildings, Computers, Food, Logos, Office, People,
            Transport, USA & World.
            (This directory also includes high resolution IFF conversions of
            all the EPS format clipart)


------------------------------------------------------------------------------


IMAGES      in IFF 16/256 and Ham interlace

Animals, Balloons, Blake7, Cars, Conan, Dragon Lance, Fantasy, Horses,
Natural, Planes, Racing, Renders, Reptiles, SnowScenes, Space, Star Trek
(TOS&Movies) Trains & 67+mb of 736 x 566 Video Backdrops in IFF 16 & 256
colour formats.


------------------------------------------------------------------------------


OTHER STUFF

All Pagestream3 updates to version 3.0H, Complete Opalvision2.3b update,
Typesmith2.5a update and Demo, Pagestream2 Demo, 18 really useful Utilities
and heaps of other stuff!


